section.t:
The option is validated by confirming that all of the
      following conditions are met:

        the option-len is greater than 3;
        the option data can be contained by the option length
          (that the option length does not run off the end of the
          packet);
        the individual label lengths do not exceed the option length;
        the tunnel-endpoint-name is of valid format as described in
        DHCPv6 Section 8 ;
        there are no compression tags;
        there is at least one label of nonzero length.

back.references:
      &rfc1034;
      &rfc1035;
